Firecrawl Skills Pack — ISC provenance

This Pi adaptation contains routing, trigger, endpoint-selection, and workflow
material adapted from official Firecrawl skill repositories. The exact upstream
revisions and adaptation boundaries are recorded in references/provenance.md.

